ements-Annuels.html?year=1999 |archivedate=February 25, 2012 }}</ref>\n|12\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|German Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/charts/album-jahr/for-date-1999 |title=Top 100 Album-Jahrescharts|language=German |publisher=[[GfK Entertainment]]|accessdate=September 8, 2016}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Swedish Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hitlistan.se/ |title=Sverigetopplistan \u2013 \u00c5rslista Album (inkl samlingar) \u2013 \u00c5r 1999 (Note: Go to S\u00f6k alla listor > \u00c5rslistor (inkl samlingar) > V\u00e4lj \u00e5r 1999 > Visa!) |work=Sverigetopplistan |accessdate=March 6, 2012 |language=Swedish |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100727130120/http://www.hitlistan.se/ |archivedate=July 27, 2010}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|34\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Swiss Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hitparade.ch/year.asp?key=1999 |title=Hitparade.ch \u2013 Schweizer Jahreshitparade 1999 |publisher=Hung Medien |accessdate=May 29, 2011 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012031724/http://hitparade.ch/year.asp?key=1999 |archivedate=October 12, 2013 }}</ref>\n|8\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|UK Albums Chart<ref>http://www.bpi.co.uk/assets/files/Yearly%20best%20sellers%20-%20albums.pdf</ref>\n|18\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|US ''Billboard'' 200<ref name=\"billboard.biz\">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/charts/yearendcharts/1999/the-billboard-200|title=Billboard.BIZ \u2013 Year-end Charts \u2013 Billboard 200 \u2013 1999\n|publisher=billboard.biz|accessdate=November 17, 2011}}</ref>\n|30\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|US R&B/Hip-Hop Albums<ref name=\"billboard.biz\"/>\n|12\n|-\n! Chart (2000) !! Position\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|US ''Billboard'' 200<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/charts/yearendcharts/2000/the-billboard-200|title=Billboard.BIZ \u2013 Year-end Charts \u2013 Billboard 200 \u2013 2000\n|publisher=billboard.biz|accessdate=Nov